{
    "chapter": 91,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "91:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以太阳盟誓，以它从东方升起的时刻盟誓。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "91:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以太阳落山后随之而来的月亮盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "91:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以用其光亮照亮大地的白昼盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "91:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以笼罩大地，使其成为黑暗的夜盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "91:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以精美的创造-苍穹盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "91:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以大地盟誓，以便于人类居于其中的平坦的大地盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "91:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以每个心灵盟誓，以真主对其均衡地创造盟誓。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "91:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主使灵魂未学而知何为毒害而避之，何为善良而从之。</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "91:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以熏陶、且摆脱了低贱而净化自己性灵者确已获取了胜利，</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "91:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>戕害内心，而使它悄悄地蒙上罪恶和过错者，确已注定失败。</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "91:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>赛莫德人否认了他们的使者撒立哈，且过度干恶和犯罪，</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "91:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当批评完他的民众之后，他们中的薄福之人站起来，</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "91:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主的使者撒立哈（愿主赐他平安）对他们说：“你们当放任真主的那头骆驼，让它自由自在地过它的日子，不要去伤害它。”</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "91:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>就骆驼一事，他们否认了他们的使者，他们中最恶的罪人杀死了那头骆驼，而他们对此表示乐意，他们都是最恶的同犯。故真主惩治了他们，因他们的罪过而以一声巨响而毁灭了他们，他们中的所有人都一并惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "91:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主对他们惩处了严厉的惩罚，祂毫不畏惧后果的毁灭了他们。</p>"
        }
    }
}